H.3 verify (2026-05-14):

Scope: workspace-fair sweep so one workspace with many active
       triggers can't monopolize the POLL_BATCH_SIZE=50 window and
       starve other workspaces. Adds a per-workspace cap (default
       5 rows/sweep) via a ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY
       workspace_id ORDER BY next_poll_at) window. Denormalizes
       workspace_id onto composio_poll_state to avoid a JOIN-per-
       sweep against automations.

